== 诊断 ==
间接免疫荧光（Indirect fluorescent antibody，IFA）检测、[[酶联免疫吸附试验|酶联免疫吸附试验]]（ELISA） 或[[聚合酶链式反应|聚合酶链式反应]]（PCR）检测<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Typhus fevers for healthcare providers|url=https://www.cdc.gov/typhus/healthcare-providers/index.html|accessdate=2021-02-27|date=2020-11-13|last=|work=|publisher=[[美国疾控中心|美国疾控中心]]|language=en-us|archive-date=2017-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170327075824/https://www.cdc.gov/typhus/healthcare-providers/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 治疗 ==
流行性斑疹伤寒感染可采用[[抗生素|抗生素]]治疗，输液和输氧也可用于稳定病人情况。无治疗的病患死亡率和经过治疗后的病患死亡率存在显著差异：无治疗的死亡率为10%-60%，而在首次感染8天内进行抗生素治疗可使得死亡率接近0%。[[多西环素|多西环素]]、[[四環黴素|四环霉素]]、[[氯霉素|氯霉素]]常被用于治疗<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Treatment of louse-borne typhus fever with chloramphenicol, tetracycline or doxycycline|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/1183367/|last=Krause|first=D. W.|last2=Perine|first2=P. L.|date=1975-08|journal=East African Medical Journal|issue=8|volume=52|pages=421–427|issn=0012-835X|pmid=1183367|last3=McDade|first3=J. E.|last4=Awoke|first4=S.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Treatment of epidemic typhus a comparative study of chloramphenicol, trimethoprim-sulphamethoxazole and doxycycline|url=https://academic.oup.com/trstmh/article/67/5/718/1930169|last=Huys|first=J.|last2=Freyens|first2=P.|date=1973-01-01|journal=Transactions of The Royal Society of Tropical Medicine and Hygiene|issue=5|doi=10.1016/0035-9203(73)90043-6|volume=67|pages=718–721|language=en|issn=0035-9203|last3=Kayihigi|first3=J.|last4=Van den Berghe|first4=G.}}</ref>。

== 流行历史 ==
