在[[第一次世界大战|第一次世界大战]]（1914–1918年）前，[[地方性斑疹伤寒|地方性斑疹伤寒]]出现于[[波兰|波兰]]及邻国<ref>{{Cite web|title=Health, Disease, Mortality; Demographic Effects {{!}} International Encyclopedia of the First World War (WW1)|url=https://encyclopedia.1914-1918-online.net/article/health_disease_mortality_demographic_effects|access-date=2021-02-26|website=encyclopedia.1914-1918-online.net|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118080257/https://encyclopedia.1914-1918-online.net/article/health_disease_mortality_demographic_effects|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Typhus Fever in Poland, 1916 to 1919.|url=https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/pdf/10.1177/003591572001301507|last=Goodall|first=E. W.|date=1920-04-23|journal=Section of Epidemiology and State Medicine|access-date=2021-02-27|archive-date=2021-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211211082701/https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/pdf/10.1177/003591572001301507|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 第一次世界大战期间，流行性斑疹伤寒在俄国可能造成了约300万人死亡，在[[波兰|波兰]]、[[罗马尼亚|罗马尼亚]]等地也有数百万平民因此丧生<ref name=":6">{{cite journal|title=Typhus and its control in Russia, 1870–1940|author=Patterson KD|journal=Med Hist|issue=4|doi=10.1017/s0025727300058725|year=1993|volume=37|pages=361–381 [378]|pmc=1036775|pmid=8246643}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Typhus, War, and Vaccines|url=https://www.historyofvaccines.org/content/blog/typhus-war-and-vaccines|language=en|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-02-26|website=History of Vaccines|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228050952/https://www.historyofvaccines.org/content/blog/typhus-war-and-vaccines}}</ref>。 1914年起，许多军人、囚犯甚至医生都受到感染，在[[塞尔维亚|塞尔维亚]]至少有15万人染病死亡，其中5万人是囚犯<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The impact of infectious disease in war time: a look back at WW1|url=https://www.futuremedicine.com/doi/full/10.2217/fmb-2018-0323|last=Pennington|first=Hugh|date=2019-01-10|journal=Future Microbiology|issue=3|doi=10.2217/fmb-2018-0323|volume=14|pages=165–168|issn=1746-0913|access-date=2021-02-27|archive-date=2021-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211211082713/https://www.futuremedicine.com/doi/full/10.2217/fmb-2018-0323|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Typhus in World War I|url=https://microbiologysociety.org/publication/past-issues/world-war-i/article/typhus-in-world-war-i.html|last=|first=|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-02-26|website=Microbiology Society|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308213901/https://microbiologysociety.org/publication/past-issues/world-war-i/article/typhus-in-world-war-i.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=A Pandemic of Typhus in Serbia in 1914 and 1915|url=https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/pdf/10.1177/003591571801101302|last=SOUBBOTITCH|first=V.|date=1917-11-30|journal=Section of Epidemiology and State Medicine|access-date=2021-02-27|archive-date=2020-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200330014529/https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/pdf/10.1177/003591571801101302|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一战的[[西方戰線_(第一次世界大戰)|西部战线]]专门为部队设有除虱站，而[[东方战线_(第一次世界大战)|东部战线]]则饱受该疾病困扰。当时该病的死亡率达10-40%，也是许多医护人员死亡的主因之一。一战和[[俄国内战|俄国内战]]期间，1918年-1922年，俄国境内共有2000-3000万人染病，其中200-300万人死亡，是历史上[[流行病列表|致死人数最多的流行病之一]]<ref name=":6" />。

[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]中，流行性斑疹伤寒也造成了数十万人死亡<ref name="Zinsser">{{cite book|last=Zinsser|first=Hans|url=https://archive.org/details/ratslicehistoryb00zins_0|title=Rats, Lice and History: A Chronicle of Pestilence and Plagues|publisher=Black Dog & Leventhal|year=1996|isbn=978-1-884822-47-6|location=New York|author-link=Hans Zinsser|orig-year=1935|url-access=registration}}</ref>。 1941年，在德军侵略[[苏联|苏联]]的[[巴巴罗萨行动|巴巴罗萨行动]]中，流行性斑疹伤寒侵袭了德军<ref name="Mazal1">{{cite book|title=Nuremberg Military Tribunal|pages=508–511|volume=I|url=http://www.mazal.org/archive/nmt/01/NMT01-T508.htm|archive-url=https://archive.is/20070701135035/http://www.mazal.org/archive/nmt/01/NMT01-T508.htm|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2007-07-01}}</ref>。 1942-43年，[[北非|北非]]和[[伊朗|伊朗]]也出现了大规模流行性斑疹伤寒疫情<ref>Zarafonetis, Chris J. D. [http://history.amedd.army.mil/booksdocs/wwii/infectiousdisvolii/chapter7.htm ''Internal Medicine in World War II, Volume II'', Chapter 7] {{Wayback|url=http://history.amedd.army.mil/booksdocs/wwii/infectiousdisvolii/chapter7.htm |date=20180707034627 }}</ref>。 在德军的[[奥斯维辛集中营|奥斯维辛集中营]]、[[贝尔根-贝尔森集中营|贝尔根-贝尔森集中营]]等地，该病也导致许多囚犯死亡<ref name="Mazal1" />。 

二战之后，随着疫苗的研发，西欧和北美地区逐渐控制了疫情。此后，该病主要在东欧、中东以及非洲部分地区出现。1993年，非洲[[蒲隆地|布隆迪]]爆发内战，出现76万难民，1995年该国的一处监狱发生大规模流行性斑疹伤寒疫情<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Outbreak of epidemic typhus associated with trench fever in Burundi|url=http://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(97)12433-3/abstract|first1=D|last2=Ndihokubwayo|first2=JB|date=1998-08-01|journal=The Lancet|issue=9125|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(97)12433-3|volume=352|pages=353–358|language=en|issn=0140-6736|pmid=9717922|last3=Tissot-Dupont|first3=H|last4=Roux|first4=V|last5=Faugere|first5=B|last6=Abegbinni|first6=R|last7=Birtles|first7=RJ|s2cid=25814472|last1=Raoult|access-date=2021-02-27|archive-date=2021-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211211082706/https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(97)12433-3/fulltext|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

